{"tid":218014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電騙停不了】42歲女中招 被騙1000萬港元","createTime":"2017-04-26T08:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T08:19:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ce62701236b9df8dd6b67ad874e5059bc5f67f6","tid":218014,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"電騙停不了，警方再接獲一名42歲姓李女子報案，指遭騙徒騙走1000萬港元。女事主較早前接獲一名不明男子來電，對方自稱為內地執法人員，指她涉嫌干犯刑事罪行， 要求她提供其內地銀行戶口資料作調查之用。女事主不虞有詐照做，結果其後發現她的內地銀行戶口內，有共約1000萬元港幣不見了，始知受騙。據悉，女事主為一名家庭主婦，家住愉景灣。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進，暫沒有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56615807&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56615807%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170426&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=04a36be4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56615807%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170426&h=03e123e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56615807&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170426</a>"},{"pid":"8ced6a671b9b5a45d2881ebab4d0f4f3c87c5809","tid":218014,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:03:11.000Z","msg":"黑錢？"},{"pid":"00f050516faa7965da4bbf5195c6884792a94297","tid":218014,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"濕碎啦住愉景灣啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c18e88ea13bf0346dfac6d5826621e3aa0f6353","tid":218014,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"1千萬唔放係香港銀行放係鄰國，點睇都唔尋常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcb8c0f543b3704c221